  "remarks": "Petropars UK Ltd. is a subsidiary of Petropars Ltd (PPL). Petropars Ltd (PPL) is wholly owned by Naftiran Intertrade Company Ltd (NICO), which belongs to the National Iranian Oil Company (NIOC), an Iranian State-owned company providing support to the Government of Iran. Therefore, Petropars UK Ltd is owned and controlled by an entity providing support to the Government of Iran.",
